# 💻 Common Maven Commands

## Compile Project

```bash
mvn compile
```

---

## Run Tests

```bash
mvn test
```

---

## Create JAR/WAR

```bash
mvn package
```

---

## Install in Local Repository

```bash
mvn install
```

---

## Clean Project

```bash
mvn clean
```

---

## Run Spring Boot Project

```bash
mvn spring-boot:run
```

---

# 🌐 Maven Repository

Maven downloads dependencies from repositories.

Types:

* Local Repository
* Central Repository
* Remote Repository

```text
Developer
    │
    ▼
Local Repository
    │
    ▼
Maven Central Repository
```

